<p><a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase/jdk15-archive-downloads.html">JDK15</a>必须是在jdk15大版本下才可以运行注册机</p>
<p><a href="https://www.52pojie.cn/thread-1369324-1-1.html">具体教程</a></p>
